                <h1>Change Your Blender Background Color in Minutes</h1>
                <p>To change the background color in Blender, first, open the "World" properties tab in the Properties panel. Look for the "Color" section; here, you can select your desired background color. Adjust the color using the color picker or manually enter RGB values. Don’t forget to render your scene to see the final look!</p>
